caption: It's hard to find an all-vegan restaurant and I'm really glad I found Soy Cafe. I like the food (the vegan cheesesteak wrap and the blue lychee smoothie are both good), the staff is kind, and the outdoor dining area is cozy. Highly recommend coming here. :)
